{
  "texts": [
    "The Baseline-AD represents the traditional approach using standard anomaly detection techniques.The process, data set, and experimental configuration utilized to assess the efficiency of the suggested algorithms will be outlined in the upcoming sections.",
    "Subsequently, the results will be scrutinized to gauge the success of each algorithm in improving the identification of anomalies in WSNs.",
    "These conclusions will offer useful perspectives to create effective and sturdy anomaly detection systems in the context of IoT and Industrial IoT applications.",
    "The proposed approach outperforms other state-of-the-art approaches in several ways.",
    "It achieves improved efficiency, enhanced resource utilization, reduced latency, lower energy consumption, enhanced scalability, improved quality of service, superior reliability, and better security and privacy measures."
  ]
}